</span></first-sel></h3><p class="sc-kAkozD iOjmJ pf-15_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Behaviour management is a crucial aspect of early years education, setting the foundation for a child's future learning and social interactions. Effective behaviour management supports a positive learning environment and fosters emotional and social development.
